{"tid":2353040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[高級哨兵]記協認為運輸署電郵通知服務無異於設立通風報信機制","createTime":"2021-01-04T12:12:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T00:22:37.000Z","uid":51271,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"47a3733a8704facf3b797d30c1210303648c7363","tid":2353040,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T12:12:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568598-20210104.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568598-20210104.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuOQDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=19585636\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568598-20210104.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=243eca46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568598-20210104.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>記者協會表示，運輸署1月2日起推出「發出車輛登記細節證明書」電郵通知服務，車主只要訂閱服務，當有人或機構申請查閱車主名下車輛證明書，運輸署會以電郵通知車主。記協認為，措施無異於設立「通風報信」機制，只要新聞工作者調查相關車輛，車主便可事先想辦法應對甚至聞風先遁，避過監察。</strong><br />\n<br />\n記協促請政府在查核車牌資料的申報選項中加入「傳媒報道」的用途，豁免此類車輛查冊的通知安排。<br />\n<br />\n記協重申，查核車牌登記是記者一貫查證手法，不少關乎重大公眾利益的報道，包括政府高官僭建及選舉舞弊等事件，均透過查核車牌及查冊方式揭露，是發揮第四權監察社會重要途徑。<br />\n<br />\n記協質疑，運輸署推出的新措施，是繼早前《鏗鏘集：7.21誰主真相》編導蔡玉玲就採訪作車輛查冊被控後，進一步打壓傳媒進行調查報道，同時亦削弱公眾的知情權。記協促請政府尊重採訪權，督促各部門開放而非收緊查冊安排。本台正向運輸署查詢。"},{"pid":"183b16f6e5dd998045b9dea37d4f2bef7e1578ff","tid":2353040,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T14:46:04.000Z","msg":"Stand News 立場新聞<br />\n <br />\nthSSponsao4rmed  &middot;<br />\n港台《鏗鏘集》編導蔡玉玲去年 11 月因查車牌被控「虛假陳述」，事發僅兩個月，運輸署再度收緊車牌查冊程序。<br />\n運輸署突然公布，由 1 月 2 日起提供新服務，透過電郵通知車主其車牌被人或機構查冊。署方晚上回覆《立場》指，該通知電郵會載列查冊人的名稱及申請目的，意味車主日後可掌握查冊者身份。署方又指，新服務推出首兩日已接 14 宗申請。<br />\n前立法會議員毛孟靜批評，車主個人資料已受《私隱條例》保障，署方新措施多此一舉，亦令因公眾利益而查冊的記者反遭「起底」，極不合理。記協批評署方尤如向受查者「通風報信」，令他們避過傳媒調查和監察。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\ncl7s"},{"pid":"f5529a36197e99dba8ae52edb120d5b2e420a3bd","tid":2353040,"uid":51271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T14:51:23.000Z","msg":"運豬署直屬狗屋"},{"pid":"2793a634a7d1e19cb44d914b531a0801047ff676","tid":2353040,"uid":248120,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T14:54:20.000Z","msg":"開巴士路綫個陣又唔見佢轉數咁快？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e41eca615d1f6b78105fc4cf1fdfccea7c47526","tid":2353040,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T15:17:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78454509ae997044ed2b9e8a434a3b393ac4e587","tid":2353040,"uid":103156,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T15:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B340aua.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB340aua.jpg&h=e8cf09f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76267bd1e087be289b5fe267f250ef3f586ab52b","tid":2353040,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T23:09:46.000Z","msg":"正苦全方位打壓記者"},{"pid":"0ed4400f3b32f6dbfb6df54a4174d6e408fcb53b","tid":2353040,"uid":267410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T23:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08321a9d5651f6a44b79315ac34844b5bce33959","tid":2353040,"uid":48624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T23:33:10.000Z","msg":"林鄭：第五權？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc8c91583bfb2325697d7384770fad98ad32c24c","tid":2353040,"uid":205967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T23:36:46.000Z","msg":"如果係班狗公開就無問題，柒婆依家不斷擺姿態同香港人講龍門任佢搬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef751c7490df8da57dadc307b4f382036f685f1","tid":2353040,"uid":49853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T00:22:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://twgreatdaily.com/images/elastic/Ahg/AhgjF24BMH2_cNUg8flB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwgreatdaily.com%2Fimages%2Felastic%2FAhg%2FAhgjF24BMH2_cNUg8flB.jpg&h=f517c720&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}